@startuml
actor "Admin" as Admin
participant "Web Frontend" as Frontend
participant "API Gateway\n(Kong)" as Kong
participant "Payment Service" as PaymentService
database "Payment DB" as DB

== Luồng 2: Lưu trữ gói thuê bao VIP (Archive Plan) ==
Admin -> Frontend: Chọn gói thuê bao VIP, bấm "Lưu trữ" (Archive/Deactivate)
activate Frontend
Frontend -> Kong: DELETE /code-payment-service/plans/{plan_id}\n[Headers: Authorization: Bearer <token>]
activate Kong
Kong -> PaymentService: Chuyển tiếp yêu cầu xóa gói thuê bao VIP
activate PaymentService

PaymentService -> DB: UPDATE Plan SET isActive=false WHERE id=planId
activate DB
DB --> PaymentService: OK (Đã lưu trữ)
deactivate DB

PaymentService --> Kong: Trả về kết quả thành công (HTTP 200 OK)
deactivate PaymentService
Kong --> Frontend: Trả về kết quả thành công
deactivate Kong
Frontend --> Admin: Hiển thị thông báo "Đã lưu trữ gói thuê bao VIP thành công"
deactivate Frontend
@enduml
